{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":308000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":323000,"text":"Thank you. Ooh, I'm like, \"Phew, phew, calm down. Get back into my body now.\" (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":328000,"text":"Usually when I play out, the first thing that happens is"},{"time":332000,"text":"people scream out, \"What's she doing?!\""},{"time":335000,"text":"I'll play at these rock shows, be on stage"},{"time":338000,"text":"standing completely still, and they're like,"},{"time":340000,"text":"\"What's she doing?! What's she doing?!\""},{"time":343000,"text":"And then I'll kind of be like -- (Vvvwow!) -- and then they're like, \"Whoa!\""},{"time":347000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":349000,"text":"I'm sure you're trying to figure out,"},{"time":353000,"text":"\"Well, how does this thing work?\""},{"time":355000,"text":"Well, what I'm doing is"},{"time":359000,"text":"controlling the pitch with my left hand."},{"time":366000,"text":"See, the closer I get to this antenna, the higher the note gets --"},{"time":371000,"text":"(Portamento) --"},{"time":374000,"text":"and you can get it really low."},{"time":376000,"text":"And with this hand I'm controlling the volume,"},{"time":379000,"text":"so the further away my right hand gets, the louder it gets."},{"time":383000,"text":"(Tones)"},{"time":386000,"text":"So basically, with both of your hands"},{"time":388000,"text":"you're controlling pitch and volume and kind of"},{"time":392000,"text":"trying to create the illusion that you're doing separate notes,"},{"time":396000,"text":"when really it's continuously going ..."},{"time":398000,"text":"(Flourish ... Beep)"},{"time":402000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":411000,"text":"Sometimes I startle myself: I'll forget that I have it on,"},{"time":413000,"text":"and I'll lean over to pick up something,"},{"time":416000,"text":"and then it goes like -- (Blip) -- \"Oh!\""},{"time":419000,"text":"And it's like a funny sound effect that follows you around"},{"time":422000,"text":"if you don't turn the thing off."},{"time":424000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":429000,"text":"Maybe we'll go into the next tune,"},{"time":433000,"text":"because I totally lost where this is going."},{"time":437000,"text":"We're going to do a song by David Mash called \"Listen: the Words Are Gone,\""},{"time":442000,"text":"and maybe I'll have words come back into me afterwards if I can relax."}]},{"cues":[{"time":446000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":620000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":632000,"text":"So, I'm trying to think of some of the questions"},{"time":635000,"text":"that are commonly asked; there are so many."},{"time":637000,"text":"And ... Well, I guess I could tell you"},{"time":640000,"text":"a little of the history of the theremin."},{"time":642000,"text":"It was invented around the 1920s, and the inventor, LÃ©on Theremin"},{"time":648000,"text":"-- he also was a musician besides an inventor --"},{"time":653000,"text":"he came up with the idea for making the theremin,"},{"time":658000,"text":"I think, when he was working on some shortwave radios."},{"time":662000,"text":"And there'd be that sound in the signal -- it's like (Screeching) --"},{"time":665000,"text":"and he thought, \"Oh, what if I could control that sound"},{"time":669000,"text":"and turn it into an instrument, because there are pitches in it.\""},{"time":673000,"text":"And so somehow through developing that,"},{"time":676000,"text":"he eventually came to make the theremin the way it is now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":683000,"text":"And a lot of times, even kids nowadays,"},{"time":687000,"text":"they'll make reference to a theremin by going, \"Whoo-hoo-hoo-hoo,\""},{"time":691000,"text":"because in the '50s it was used in the sci-fi horror movies,"},{"time":693000,"text":"that sound that's like ... (Woo-hoo-hoo-hoo)"},{"time":697000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":700000,"text":"It's kind of a funny, goofy sound to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":706000,"text":"And sometimes if I have too much coffee,"},{"time":708000,"text":"then my vibrato gets out of hand."},{"time":710000,"text":"You're really sensitive to your body and its functions"},{"time":713000,"text":"when you're behind this thing."},{"time":715000,"text":"You have to stay so still if you want to have the most control."},{"time":718000,"text":"It reminds me of the balancing act earlier on -- what Michael was doing --"},{"time":723000,"text":"because you're fighting so hard to keep the balance"},{"time":726000,"text":"with what you're playing with and stay in tune, and at the same time"},{"time":732000,"text":"you don't want to focus so much on being in tune all the time;"},{"time":735000,"text":"you want to be feeling the music."}]},{"cues":[{"time":738000,"text":"And then also, you're trying to stay very, very, very still"},{"time":742000,"text":"because little movements with other parts of your body"},{"time":746000,"text":"will affect the pitch, or sometimes if you're holding a low note -- (Tone rising out of key) --"},{"time":753000,"text":"and breathing will make it ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":756000,"text":"(Laughter)\n"}]},{"cues":[{"time":757000,"text":"If I pass out on the next song ..."},{"time":760000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":762000,"text":"I think of it almost like"},{"time":766000,"text":"like a yoga instrument because it makes you so aware"},{"time":769000,"text":"of every little crazy thing your body is doing,"},{"time":773000,"text":"or just aware of what you don't want it to be doing"},{"time":778000,"text":"while you're playing; you don't want to have any sudden movements."},{"time":782000,"text":"And if I go to a club and play a gig, people are like,"},{"time":785000,"text":"\"Here, have some drinks on us!\""},{"time":787000,"text":"And it's like, \"Well, I'm about to go on soon;"},{"time":790000,"text":"I don't want to be like -- (Teetering tones) -- you know?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":794000,"text":"It really does reflect the mood that you're in also,"},{"time":797000,"text":"if you're ..."},{"time":799000,"text":"it's similar to being a vocalist, except"},{"time":802000,"text":"instead of it coming out of your throat,"},{"time":804000,"text":"you're controlling it just in the air"},{"time":806000,"text":"and you don't really have a point of reference;"},{"time":809000,"text":"you're always relying on your ears and adjusting constantly."},{"time":814000,"text":"You just have to always adjust to what's happening"},{"time":816000,"text":"and realize you'll have bummer notes come here and there"},{"time":820000,"text":"and listen to it, adjust it, and just move on,"},{"time":823000,"text":"or else you'll get too tied up and go crazy. Like me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":832000,"text":"I think we will play another tune now."},{"time":837000,"text":"I'm going to do \"Lush Life.\" It's one of my favorite tunes to play."}]},{"cues":[{"time":840000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1130000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}